org.jsonurl

Interface ExceptionProvider

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    JsonUrlIterator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEventIterator

    public interface ExceptionProvider
    An instance of this interface can create parse, limit, and syntax exceptions with parser-specific position information.
    Since:
    2020-11-01
    Author:
    jsonurl.org, David MacCormack
